> Warhead: If you're not interested, then too bad for you. I'm not going
> to keep some for anyone who isn't a true Predacon!
>

{Nightshade}

    Chuckling as she stood at the door she looked back over her shoulder
plate, "You be amusin darlin, now I be seein why Megatron keeps you around."
Turning she walked back through the door heading to the CR chambers. Upon
arrival she quickly scans for a suitable alternate form, settling on a
silver fox.

    After a few minutes she steps from the chamber and poses before the
reflective surface of another chamber, "Mmmmm ma'volous." Turning she slowly
walked from the room to report for this "duty" ignoring the maximal rifles
keeping only her own weaponry on hand.
